Interface EnhancementParameters

  • All Superinterfaces:
    NamespaceCalculator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultEnhancementParameters

    public interface EnhancementParameters
extends NamespaceCalculator
    Interface to provide CSVtoRDF the interpretation guidance it needs. Abstracts away the enhancement parameter encoding.
